.TH "LIGHTNING-NODE-LISTFORWARDS-IN-OUT-DIFF" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-node-listforwards-in-out-diff \- FEAT-2960 node-listforwards-in-out-diff
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning node-listforwards-in-out-diff
.SH DESCRIPTION
Computes the difference between total in_msat and out_msat of settled forwards for the lightning CLI (FEAT-2960).
.PP
Output: JSON from CLN with key \fBin_out_diff_msat\fR.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
